ygData.messageBody:
I'm progressing pretty well in Prexus so far. With the experiences as a
wiz in Innoruuk, my Prexus wiz is created with a better stats, better
managed and better trained . Btw, when I login around 9-10pm last night,
Prexus was the 2nd least crowded server on the list.

As in UO, many of us dunno what we wanna be when we first enter the world
of Britannia. After sometime, we more or less settled with down what we
wanna be (just like in RL). I myself is kinda half hearted initially in
Innoruuk coz of the hard life of a wiz. Now I think I would love to be one
and settled as one ;)

Mondain (Gnomish Wizard, Prexus)
